  "description": "Use this skill when designing or querying the NPSP data model \u2014 constituent 360, household accounts, giving history rollups, and program participation. Trigger keywords: NPSP data model, household account, constituent record, giving rollups, CRLP, program engagement, ServiceDelivery, npo02__ fields. NOT for standard data model design, Nonprofit Cloud (NPC) data model, FSC household groups, or platform data modeling outside the NPSP context.",
